        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Zero-Emission Homes Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of Energy to establish a Zero-Emission Homes Program that provides rebates to homeowners and owners of multifamily buildings for qualified electrification projects (e.g., electric stoves or heat pumps).</p>]]>
        </text>
